title: Spectator Out Loud: Revd Marcus Walker, Douglas Murray and Petronella Wyatt
description:
On this week's episode: 

Revd Marcus Walker shares his concern and disapproval at being described by the Church of England as an 'Key Limiting Factor' (00:26). 
Then Douglas Murray looks at the tricky subject of transracialism (09:48)
And finally Petronella Wyatt gives her two cents on modern day Westminster culture (17:15).

Presented by Sam Holmes
